{"title":"第一个Servlet程序：HelloWorld","uid":"3469f91a90a432395e3467ad508f6c20","slug":"第一个Servlet程序：HelloWorld","date":"2023-06-17T13:04:13.000Z","updated":"2023-06-17T15:13:23.956Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/第一个Servlet程序：HelloWorld.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<h1 id=\"第一个Servlet程序：Hello-World\"><a href=\"#第一个Servlet程序：Hello-World\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"第一个Servlet程序：Hello World\"></a>第一个Servlet程序：Hello World</h1><p>我们先创建一个Java Web的项目。我这里使用的IDE是IntelliJ IDEA 2021.3.3 (Ultimate Edition)。</p>\n<ol>\n<li>创建Java EE项目</li>\n</ol>\n<p><img src=\"/../images/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AAServlet%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%EF%BC%9AHelloWorld/image-20230617224322068.png\" alt=\"image-20230617224322068\"></p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>选择JavaEE的版本</li>\n</ol>\n<p><img src=\"/../images/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AAServlet%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%EF%BC%9AHelloWorld/image-20230617224530902.png\" alt=\"image-20230617224530902\"></p>\n<p>因为我的Tomcat版本是10，所以我选择Jakata EE 9。</p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>点击完成之后得到下面的目录</li>\n</ol>\n<p><img src=\"/../images/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AAServlet%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%EF%BC%9AHelloWorld/image-20230617224613498.png\" alt=\"image-20230617224613498\"></p>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>配置Tomcat</li>\n</ol>\n<p><img src=\"/../images/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AAServlet%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%EF%BC%9AHelloWorld/image-20230617224643423.png\" alt=\"image-20230617224643423\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/../images/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AAServlet%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%EF%BC%9AHelloWorld/image-20230617224715989.png\" alt=\"image-20230617224715989\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/../images/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AAServlet%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%EF%BC%9AHelloWorld/image-20230617224738359.png\" alt=\"image-20230617224738359\"></p>\n<ol start=\"5\">\n<li>编写程序，IDEA默认生成了</li>\n</ol>\n<p>index.jsp：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-jsp\" data-language=\"jsp\"><code class=\"language-jsp\">&lt;%@ page contentType&#x3D;&quot;text&#x2F;html; charset&#x3D;UTF-8&quot; pageEncoding&#x3D;&quot;UTF-8&quot; %&gt;\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\n&lt;html&gt;\n&lt;head&gt;\n    &lt;title&gt;JSP - Hello World&lt;&#x2F;title&gt;\n&lt;&#x2F;head&gt;\n&lt;body&gt;\n&lt;h1&gt;&lt;%&#x3D; &quot;Hello World!&quot; %&gt;\n&lt;&#x2F;h1&gt;\n&lt;br&#x2F;&gt;\n&lt;a href&#x3D;&quot;hello-servlet&quot;&gt;Hello Servlet&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\n    &lt;font color&#x3D;&quot;red&quot;&gt;这里是JSP页面&lt;&#x2F;font&gt;\n&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;\n&lt;&#x2F;body&gt;\n&lt;&#x2F;html&gt;</code></pre>\n\n<p>HelloServlet.java：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-java\" data-language=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java\">package cn.cukor.javawebstudy;\n\nimport java.io.*;\n\nimport jakarta.servlet.http.*;\nimport jakarta.servlet.annotation.*;\n\n@WebServlet(name &#x3D; &quot;helloServlet&quot;, value &#x3D; &quot;&#x2F;hello-servlet&quot;)\npublic class HelloServlet extends HttpServlet &#123;\n    private String message;\n\n    public void init() &#123;\n        message &#x3D; &quot;这里是Servlet页面!&quot;;\n    &#125;\n\n    public void doGet(HttpServletRequest request, HttpServletResponse response) throws IOException &#123;\n        response.setContentType(&quot;text&#x2F;html&quot;);\n\n        &#x2F;&#x2F; Hello\n        PrintWriter out &#x3D; response.getWriter();\n        out.println(&quot;&lt;html&gt;&lt;body&gt;&quot;);\n        out.println(&quot;&lt;h1&gt;&quot; + message + &quot;&lt;&#x2F;h1&gt;&quot;);\n        out.println(&quot;&lt;&#x2F;body&gt;&lt;&#x2F;html&gt;&quot;);\n    &#125;\n\n    public void destroy() &#123;\n    &#125;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<p>因为使用了注解，所以<code>web.xml</code>中就不需要做其他工作。</p>\n<ol start=\"5\">\n<li>运行项目</li>\n</ol>\n<p><img src=\"/../images/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AAServlet%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%EF%BC%9AHelloWorld/image-20230617224806701.png\" alt=\"image-20230617224806701\"></p>\n<ol start=\"6\">\n<li>运行效果</li>\n</ol>\n<p><img src=\"/../images/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AAServlet%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%EF%BC%9AHelloWorld/image-20230617231113346.png\" alt=\"image-20230617231113346\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/../images/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AAServlet%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%EF%BC%9AHelloWorld/image-20230617231126313.png\" alt=\"image-20230617231126313\"></p>\n","feature":true,"text":"第一个Servlet程序：Hello World我们先创建一个Java Web的项目。我这里使用的IDE是IntelliJ IDEA 2021.3.3 (Ultimate Edition)。 创建Java EE项目 选择JavaEE的版本 因为我的Tomcat版本是10，所以我选...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.8k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"Java","slug":"Java","count":16,"path":"api/tags/Java.json"},{"name":"Servlet","slug":"Servlet","count":2,"path":"api/tags/Servlet.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AAServlet%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%EF%BC%9AHello-World\"><span class=\"toc-text\">第一个Servlet程序：Hello World</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"CukorZhong","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/images/logo.jpg","link":"/","description":"一个对计算机技术非常热爱的程序员","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":"/images/bilibili-svgrepo-com.svg","link":"https://space.bilibili.com/1117276308"},"csdn":{"icon":"/images/csdn.svg","link":"https://blog.csdn.net/qq_53744721"}}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{},"next_post":{"title":"Servet简介","uid":"c7fd338c728a9814bfec7f21fbca8c5a","slug":"Servet简介","date":"2023-06-17T12:41:28.000Z","updated":"2023-06-17T13:02:15.305Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Servet简介.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"text":"Servlet简介Servlet（服务器端小程序）是使用Java语言编写的服务器端程序，可以像JSP一样，生成动态的Web页面，Servlet主要运行在服务器端，并由服务器调用执行，是一种按照Servlet标准开发的类。 Servlet程序是Java对CGI程序的实现，但是与传统...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":633,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"Java","slug":"Java","count":16,"path":"api/tags/Java.json"},{"name":"Servlet","slug":"Servlet","count":2,"path":"api/tags/Servlet.json"}],"author":{"name":"CukorZhong","slug":"blog-autho